    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you answer for your crimes? For making mistakes that can't be undone? For creating something that shouldn't exist? This situation is a good opportunity to test that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your task is to erase the traces, destroy what was born within these cold walls, and regain control. Use everything you can get your hands on and get ready to do your best to fix your own nightmare. Make sure you do it before it's too late. There can be no mistakes - now you must face the creation of your greatest fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/e72f1bb29cda74f65eb84fd88151e533.avif?t=1772015895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras_big/e72f1bb29cda74f65eb84fd88151e533.avif?t=1772015895 width=800 height=88 /></span><strong>Use  stationary devices to work with ingredients. Combine them according to recipes or experiment — who knows where that may lead.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/d0c4c3c157123a5544c629ebafb24262.poster.avif?t=1772015895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/d0c4c3c157123a5544c629ebafb24262.webm?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/d0c4c3c157123a5544c629ebafb24262.mp4?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/88ff9125c0f2006ffb68676396249cc0.avif?t=1772015895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras_big/88ff9125c0f2006ffb68676396249cc0.avif?t=1772015895 width=800 height=88 /></span><strong>Find and use handy items to gain some advantages. Determine whether capacity, stealth, maneuverability, or something else is more important to you.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/1edcd8edb1aa88980fda59771c607ec4.poster.avif?t=1772015895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/1edcd8edb1aa88980fda59771c607ec4.webm?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/1edcd8edb1aa88980fda59771c607ec4.mp4?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/e3efd48e492bdbc1bbc2755d526829e3.avif?t=1772015895\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras_big/e3efd48e492bdbc1bbc2755d526829e3.avif?t=1772015895 width=800 height=88 /></span><strong>Monitor the generator's condition. Adjust the power load to conserve energy, even if it means sacrificing parts of the facility’s functionality. Remember — without electricity, you won’t survive.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/87b14aa35a5f1eae89fec632bda5f359.poster.avif?t=1772015895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/87b14aa35a5f1eae89fec632bda5f359.webm?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/87b14aa35a5f1eae89fec632bda5f359.mp4?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/dccdc68883578e59cf33f08794f96188.avif?t=1772015895\" width=1280 height=140 /></span><strong>Your adversary has sharp hearing and incredible speed. Any sound could give away your position. Be careful — he's far smarter and deadlier than he appears at first glance. Who knows what else he’s capable of?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/846b2897879a4efa4cbcc04da82fbf30.poster.avif?t=1772015895\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/846b2897879a4efa4cbcc04da82fbf30.webm?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138910/extras/846b2897879a4efa4cbcc04da82fbf30.mp4?t=1772015895\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>These features allow every player to find their own style and strategy for completing the game, generating different situations during gameplay.</strong></i></p>",
